name: MultipleGestationICD10CM
title: Multiple Gestation ICD10CM
purpose: (Clinical Focus: This set of  values contains diagnoses that represent the delivery of twins and higher order multiples.),(Data Element Scope: The intent of this data element is to identify patients who delivered twins or higher order of multiples. Using the Quality Data Model, this particular element will map to the Diagnosis category or the Diagnosis attribute for the Encounter category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Include ICD10CM codes that identify a delivery of twins or higher order multiples.),(Exclusion Criteria: Exclude codes that do not meet the inclusion criteria.)
